            "id": 6425978,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 金居(8358)股價拉至漲停，漲停價404.0元，成交48,958張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金居(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8358:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8358\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8358-TW</a>)20日11:28上漲36.5元，股價漲停報404.0元，委買8,980,000張，成交48,958張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為CC01080電子零組件製造業。CA04010金屬表面處理業。CA01110鍊銅業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金居(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8358:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8358\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8358-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲34.37%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.54%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+22,529 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+15,158 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+6,768 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+603 張</li> <li>融資增減：-438 張</li> <li>融券增減：+2,019 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
